License to Drive is a 1988 teen adventure film written by Neil Tolkin and directed by Greg Beeman in his feature film directorial debut .
It stars Corey Haim , Corey Feldman , Heather Graham , Carol Kane , Richard Masur , Michael Manasseri and Nina Siemaszko .
The film was in production in late 1987 .
It was released on July 6 , 1988 in the United States and grossed over $ 20 million at the North American box office .
It was distributed by 20th Century Fox .